== version 0.2.4 ==

- Drag&Drop insert of directories as zipped files
- Optional syntax highliting in pastebin
- Remember window position over program restart
- Fix errors with unicode filenames
- Default file insert priority set to LOW

== version 0.2.3 ==

- "Open in Browser" now works for https if configured in settings.
- Better pattern to recognize freenet keys.
- New Icons
- Keep-alive requests to prevent socket timeouts to node.
- Pastebin doesn't allow pastes in disconnected state any more.
- Application Title and Icon for taskbar
